# Local-only test suite: fast unit tests that run against a minimal HA stub
# without installing Home Assistant (kept out of the repo). The committed
# CI test suite lives in /tests/ and runs against real Home Assistant on
# GitHub Actions (see .github/workflows/test.yaml).
/tests_local/

# Local-only CLI debug tool and its output (hits the real portal;
